{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"213354-the-peacock-s-dance","title":"The Peacock's Dance","description":"Hina went to the farm with her father one day. She saw a peacock dancing and started to dance as well. How did the peacock react? Read more to find out.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kaminee Singh"],"illustrators":["Partho Sengupta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Education Foundation","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/213354-the-peacock-s-dance"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/285296/size3/fdb378a472f71021e971a650d68c810b.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/285296/size6/fdb378a472f71021e971a650d68c810b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280300/size6/b698aaa3a863d94cf9e8789364e80931.jpg","text":"Hina\nwent to the farm with her father.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280303/size6/b4de7f23daf57c3405d281a8480ff69b.jpg","text":"Her\nfather got busy with his work. Hina started walking in the farm.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280306/size6/76631365aee932f6b84f4d5eb99b05e8.jpg","text":"She\nsaw a peacock in the farm. \nShe started walking towards the peacock.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280308/size6/8a16dee388c48fe7292ec1fddbd27a37.jpg","text":"Suddenly, it started raining lightly.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280313/size6/8c178aa64bd84a20cea3bcc8778a5ade.jpg","text":"Seeing\nthe rain, the peacock started dancing.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280316/size6/d50ea5cac72a7faa78c9af252b4ce86d.jpg","text":"Seeing the peacock, Hina also started dancing.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280320/size6/3aafd58e9dd070830c8064b5ad675314.jpg","text":"The\npeacock forgot to dance.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/280323/size6/b8807a613af67513aceceb27fb0713e1.jpg","text":"It just stood there watching Hina dance!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":65}}